The 150k pound Orbiter, the 65k pound payload
dictated the requirements of the Orbiter injected

00:25:10.710 --> 00:25:11.710
weight.

00:25:11.710 --> 00:25:12.710
You add them up.

00:25:12.710 --> 00:25:14.429
You've got to get it into orbit.

