00:28:55.740 --> 00:28:59.679
CFD gets it right every now and then.

00:28:59.679 --> 00:29:03.220
Sometimes it doesn't get it right.

00:29:03.220 --> 00:29:07.750
And the wind tunnel test still hadn't got
