The flight data is used, and we update that.

00:29:17.470 --> 00:29:18.590
Yes, sir.

00:29:18.590 --> 00:29:22.139
When you say flare angle, do you mean like
in the stack away from the Orbiter?

00:29:22.139 --> 00:29:23.139
Yes, sir.

00:29:23.139 --> 00:29:25.039
This flare angle right back here.

00:29:25.039 --> 00:29:33.490
We found that if you set that right, it pretty
well sets the flow and the plumes behave themselves.

00:29:33.490 --> 00:29:39.441
If you set that too small the plumes will
