[LAUGHTER] That's pretty much like a vehicle
that is kind of trimmed out of a piece of

00:33:50.760 --> 00:33:54.900
a sphere, if you please.

00:33:54.900 --> 00:34:05.190
And those aerodynamic characteristics were
very good.

