As a matter of fact, the thing is laid out
on graph paper and you counted the squares

00:34:13.470 --> 00:34:16.850
and saw where the CG was and what things had
to be.

00:34:16.850 --> 00:34:17.940
And it worked.

00:34:17.940 --> 00:34:18.940
It worked.

